full_address: Lot 9/41- 43 Manitzky Road, Tamborine Mountain, Qld 4272
description:
Perfectly positioned in the exclusive Blue Wing Estate, this lush and affordable 5.5 acre allotment is your golden chance to secure a blue-chip piece of beautiful Tamborine Mountain.

Serviced by a sealed driveway with on-site power and bore; this stunning whisper-quiet hobby farm site offers rich fertile soil and unparalleled privacy overlooking majestic rainforest, freshwater creeks and national park.

Lot 9 features –

- 22,210 m2 of prime gently elevated land

- One of only 4 exclusive acreage Lots

- Power, bore and bitumen driveway

- Overlooking seasonal creek and rainforest, with all-day breezes and your own avocado orchard with potential to build your own dam/pond (STCA)

- Only minutes to the local IGA, coffee shops and the gorgeous Tamborine Mountain village

- Just a short drive to the stunning beaches of Surfers Paradise

- Simply bring your imagination, and build your family dream escape today

The perfect hinterland haven, the boutique Blue Wing Estate is situated an easy drive to Gold Coast city and offers a lush and peaceful getaway for sustainable hobby farming, entertaining and recreational space for all of the family to enjoy.
